  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-57c5aa6b-4305-4483-96c4-fe72cef512f6\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n\n                                <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module se-module-image __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\" \" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-57c5aa6b-4305-4483-96c4-fe72cef512f6\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4055f9a97b5e0fb9.jpg\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4055f9a97b5e0fb9.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4055f9a97b5e0fb9.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"331\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                </a>                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-71199a71-698a-48a1-a743-2a278d042687\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e243c80b-9557-472a-9288-4aef596e2b57\">남성갱년기(andropause)</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f15b0519-757e-43b9-8f40-c53224d2267f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b3fe8043-7d1a-450f-a73f-cd78c9e67426\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6e0e9c92-7c19-4d8e-b7c2-a0f679453ebb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-73403ada-60de-4737-a69b-ee3443004602\">​</span></p></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-62db4a4f-ddf1-40ac-91fe-ae21150aea2f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-36563c25-0e95-4109-a98a-f2bb86405b62\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7f3306ed-9bf2-4fbd-9cdb-d0dcbe81f3f4\">최근 ‘미운 우리 새끼’라는 TV프로그램에서 출연 연예인들이 남성호르몬 결과를 보고 일부는 기뻐하고 일부는 좌절을 했던 내용이 나왔습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-40245020-b73b-4740-be83-321420d661a1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7199782d-6568-40b6-8b3e-eedb7925af8c\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b4dae312-a902-4212-882c-b741e8aaa15c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-28483332-9b94-4969-8557-77f09b483566\">남성호르몬이 뭐길래 결과에 따라서 기뻐하기도 하고 좌절하기도 한 건지 경희이수한의원에서 알려드리겠습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cf0491a7-8158-4f6b-9ad5-09fa5c7e936f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c86e20c7-fd86-488f-b37d-9b8026696f8d\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2c114d6b-e080-4b64-a6a0-1ec0985fd93c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d712301d-2096-4f50-9bd3-021a4a7e6d15\">여성호르몬과 갱년기에 대해서는 많이 들어보고 정보도 가지고 있을 텐데 최근에 부각되고 있는 남성호르몬과 남성갱년기에 대해서는 생소한 분들이 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-eb977359-8500-469a-8c8a-5e354a450ba9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-03abf053-7600-493a-866b-9cc6a55aba03\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-019fbeca-3a9e-4872-9fc6-6fb801ab1080\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-668ac890-4cc2-436f-b727-c1492471e172\">남성호르몬에는 여러가지 종류가 있는데 주로 고환에서 분비되는 테스토스테론이 중요한 역할을 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-99bb25cd-461e-4dba-94af-5aaff87edf60\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-678c5607-7450-4389-b63f-16885b3ee630\">남성에게 있어 테스토스테론은 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0f7d1a05-5579-47de-a73e-8fb94a5ba0fe\"><b>성기능을 비롯한 활력, 심혈관, 근육, 기분</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0ed60a23-5b4e-4f07-a6d2-8b52c08250f1\">에 이르기까지 온몸에 영향을 주는 호르몬입니다. 남성호르몬은 30대 중반을 넘어가면서 매년 조금씩 감소하여 50대를 전후해서 감소 속도가 급격히 빨라지면서 갱년기 증상을 겪게 됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c28c9e9b-0e95-45a0-959f-0e3af11c3ee3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fbced6ef-f8b1-42ea-acf7-043f0e7c6460\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-89cef7a0-05d1-4131-9c77-5897264c021f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6b3e5324-78b5-4ae8-ac0d-a89e09536788\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0466ba1f-0014-4b86-bdb8-e118ca44ca45\">남성 갱년기 증상</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1e1c270d-fb33-4e15-bcb5-9a250886bed9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a3776662-47b9-4fd9-b4f3-3ff06126ddc7\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8af12c3f-5ed8-4e14-bd13-0fe00d33bdbc\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-aea3066e-c06e-4ac2-85c7-7d156acf46aa\"> </span><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-854ca291-1236-4bc6-bac0-a58fc477a5e5\">심리적 증상:중력 저하, 불안, 우울, 불면, 자신감 결여</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-81bd484b-ed64-4423-aa18-33a0d0f2bc3e\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-8437a99a-9d5b-4263-9d0b-6da6f9ab1241\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e20ded12-865d-4fa5-96d8-2d100ff25c4a\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-210906a3-cd68-4077-8c39-1e763a6868c0\">육체적 증상: 피로, 무기력, 식욕저하, 복부비만, 탈모, 관절통, 피부노화</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-472a8211-46a3-4ae8-b928-4574a448605f\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-e4925f07-c7b1-421c-af56-2f91421bd98c\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e7febd65-b173-429e-a206-d65ac3b0a12c\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-1b7b4b03-da0f-4d83-84e3-5f73b46c9abf\">성욕변화: 성욕감소, 발기부전, 성적쾌감감소</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9a4c94fa-171e-4ecb-bf8b-9b25939f7063\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-5b0aa579-6b15-4629-98a4-f8b17aedb196\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1f6da4b8-6e6c-45e8-b10c-370cf3c92e70\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-d5ee2c52-d365-4ee0-98e6-90a05b840f38\">심혈관계 증상: 안면홍조, 심계항진, 발한</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4ce57eec-075a-41ff-9cb2-d1c7fd7dc863\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n\n                                <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module se-module-image __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\" \" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-4ce57eec-075a-41ff-9cb2-d1c7fd7dc863\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxOTAxMThfMjQg/MDAxNTQ3Nzk0ODc3MDEx.JAPa9QILJVjBz0GRB68D07OXWVPDGtPhD4B1QjkghFIg.PCMy4w3gof8MTxQY9fj71fBAT_lRnGpc7spVUF11hf4g.JPEG.isuhani/Andropause-Symptoms.jpg\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxOTAxMThfMjQg/MDAxNTQ3Nzk0ODc3MDEx.JAPa9QILJVjBz0GRB68D07OXWVPDGtPhD4B1QjkghFIg.PCMy4w3gof8MTxQY9fj71fBAT_lRnGpc7spVUF11hf4g.JPEG.isuhani/Andropause-Symptoms.jpg?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxOTAxMThfMjQg/MDAxNTQ3Nzk0ODc3MDEx.JAPa9QILJVjBz0GRB68D07OXWVPDGtPhD4B1QjkghFIg.PCMy4w3gof8MTxQY9fj71fBAT_lRnGpc7spVUF11hf4g.JPEG.isuhani/Andropause-Symptoms.jpg?type=w580\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"300\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                </a>                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5b2c1016-9399-4766-9145-1269fb2a53a3\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-36c4a6c1-d2dc-459f-95f5-8654919ed649\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0f4e9f72-d1b6-4b78-89ee-b35e939b7346\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5a70d2b3-45be-4070-ac3b-20c605f108cd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3131cebc-77f8-4ddc-9dfc-c92d9d3359d5\">혈액검사상 남성호르몬 수치가 떨어진 것으로 나오면 양방병원에서는 주사제를 권합니다. 물론 주사를 맞게 되면 수치가 오르고 이로 인해 남성갱년기 증상이 일시적으로 좋아질 겁니다. 하지만 시간이 지나면 다시 수치가 떨어질 수 있으며 근본치료가 아닙니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-acdbe478-9c28-4780-aa2f-7a1bb95cbc12\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4a5b7da1-ca88-436f-99b0-df829d6e0acc\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ffb38a03-9b53-4aa4-8e03-a175335fd371\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d9abd041-5bf4-4d30-87e9-ece0532901da\">경희이수한의원에서는 진료를 통해 각각의 원인을 찾아내고 1:1 맞춤 처방을 합니다.  약해진 남성의 양기를 보하고 신장의 기운을 단단하게 해 주는 것을 기본으로 개개인에 맞는  한약치료와  침치료를 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e05aa139-e2b2-4d79-b116-522aacf9b1c3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-58cf55e9-ba6a-4ed3-9d59-ef6887cc92f0\">단순히 보양식품이나 산수유, 흑마늘 등과 같은 건강보조식품과는 차원이 다른 효과를 보실 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b5e74ce6-7d17-4f75-b718-4ddfbf3a332f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-09705950-635e-4c2d-8889-a5b3b42e5821\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7c8049b0-b846-4aab-afaf-1ad7fab39d29\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-cc1f2acb-5985-4987-a509-1dedccc215ce\">가장의 책임감으로 인한 스트레스에 지친 우리의 남편, 아버지들에게 활기와 건강을 되찾아주길 바랍니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-96d7689f-703b-4951-b792-8320f1b8b63a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n\n                                <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module se-module-image __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\" \" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-96d7689f-703b-4951-b792-8320f1b8b63a\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/525efe07cf53015b.jpg\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/525efe07cf53015b.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/525efe07cf53015b.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"333\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                </a>                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c2dc1936-236b-4aeb-8c05-7661d276d0b6\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0a213841-4bb0-4931-aa59-7c2818bac892\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-20da33ba-f446-4e30-89af-e0cc38f90e05\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b5aa0256-5f4c-44b3-80b7-1b92e33386ac\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a1f63983-92d2-4151-9537-34ffc510abf9\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>    </div>",
